{"tid":2226042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人都係咁⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-10-01T18:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T07:29:43.000Z","uid":162873,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b21287c23455bbaf89c15ae4de398ae5184e7924","tid":2226042,"uid":162873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"廿到尾朋友都冇幾個<br />\n放工星期六日淨係留喺屋企打機鳩hea<br />\n要兩老買埋嘢俾佢食<br />\n兩老有咩要佢做就推個大佬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家務從來唔做<br />\n屋企有咩缺乏從來唔會買 亦唔會夾錢<br />\n電器寛頻壞咗唔搵人整 寧願唔用等到其他人處理<br />\n屋企所有嘅責任都唔關佢事 大家有份用 佢唔識佢亦唔會處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢用你啲嘢就得 你用佢啲嘢就斤斤計較俾說話你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做少少野就覺得自己好大付出 話返你唔做嘢 洗咗一次衫就成撚日提住 證明自己有做嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明死毒撚一個但有莫明嘅自信 <br />\n之但係講嘢頭盔又戴到落地核<br />\n個人肥矮着衫又柒 完全冇自知之明<br />\n將肥肉當肌肉仲當自己大隻佬<br />\n你講嘢留有餘地唔批評佢減低佢自尊 佢就真係以為自己好靚仔好有taste<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講嘢串柒柒最鍾意人身攻擊<br />\n你廢鳩事理佢 佢會以為自己講啱咗懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日煽風點火 兩老有嘢佢睇唔過眼 會煽動呀哥出去同兩老嘈 佢自己就食花生<br />\n最鍾意包拗頸 仲以為自己好撚幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩老唔想家嘈屋閉 你挑起問題會話返你轉頭 然後話三姑六婆啲仔女幾生性 你哋成舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你哋老母啦 個仔咁矜貴你哋照顧飽佢啦 我依家搬走放長雙眼睇你哋個乖仔點孝順呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9017a644967336c7e25221ae6e0318d9f42d3d2","tid":2226042,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"搬走啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSCQ67Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSCQ67Y.jpg&h=1754748e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4552aa903a5ba945a3cac9d133933b3fa4b2c56c","tid":2226042,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"樓主好似講係我咁　"},{"pid":"d7c1f58d6c794ea39bd57069ee3407f6c0738a05","tid":2226042,"uid":162873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9017a644967336c7e25221ae6e0318d9f42d3d2","tid":2226042,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"搬走啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSCQ67Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSCQ67Y.jpg&h=1754748e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"月尾走啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d388f603207ac734d447b520f6efcbbee2a8de","tid":2226042,"uid":162873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4552aa903a5ba945a3cac9d133933b3fa4b2c56c","tid":2226042,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"樓主好似講係我咁　"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8643126d8357c4197a93bbd9d51f0aa89718a1a","tid":2226042,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"件垃圾兩老都有份縱容出嚟<br />\n<br />\n記得狠心d以後剩係比食物孝敬吓算<br />\n一定唔好比現金"},{"pid":"2575286fa73e60600cc62f8c8be6c1464e393c47","tid":2226042,"uid":199456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"記住你無欠佢地"},{"pid":"5f3b4408801d5dfcc869358624ae2f4772f46411","tid":2226042,"uid":379117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"534d01bca0386f441c50c750c8d1cd8075fbcf40","tid":2226042,"uid":162873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8643126d8357c4197a93bbd9d51f0aa89718a1a","tid":2226042,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi